14... Nc7 $1 $146 {This new move is critical and it is probably a
matter of time until someone plays it in a real game.} ({GM Hjartarsson
prepared the pawn push with} 14... Qe8 15. h5 b5 {and got a decent position in
the game Cheparinov, I (2691)-Hjartarson, J (2530) Caleta ENG 2019 1-0 (28).
