some strong players have traded queens here, (counting on a small plus in the
endgame), keeping queens on the board with} 14. Qd2 {seems to be a better
solution since Black may not find good employment for his queen in this
structure, while White may use his queen for an attack against the slightly
weakened black kingside. For example:} Nf6 15. Nd5 $1 Nxd5 16. exd5 $14 *

